description.p:
In a particular embodiment, the step of processing the authority use data in accordance with the authority choice, to obtain the authority confidence value and the initial authority choice comprises:
de-noising processing the authority use data;
performing a SVM training on the de-noised authority use data respectively in accordance with two authority choices of permission and rejection in the authority option, to obtain the authority confidence value and the initial authority choice of the corresponding authority option. In the present invention, "de-noising data" refers to removing noise data and invalid data, which may use a de-noising manner based on wavelet analysis or an offline curve de-noising manner, and the specific de-noising manner is not limited in this solution.

