The present disclosure provides a system for managing an authority, including:
a first processor; and
a memory for storing instructions executed by the first processor;
wherein the first processor is configured to:
acquire authority use data of a user from a cloud;
process the authority use data to obtain an authority result; and
send the authority result obtained by the processing to a terminal, for the terminal to update a corresponding authority option; and
a second processor; and
a memory for storing instructions executed by the second processor;
wherein the second processor is configured to:
receive an authority result sent from a server;
acquire configuration information of a corresponding authority according to the authority result; and
update a corresponding authority option according to the configuration information corresponding to the current authority.

